{"tid":843602,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸寸伊巴500球：你很老！","createTime":"2018-10-01T09:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:34:38.000Z","uid":161311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a53b8fe71156da41de05ab37def1851a3c950253","tid":843602,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=gyT6NCKs291rbtPbCDDifkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=44c8cc4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】好友就是怎樣說笑也可以。碧咸周一在網上嘲笑攻入500球的伊巴謙莫域真的太老了。<br />\n<br />\n36歲老將伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）周六為洛杉磯銀河作客FC多倫多，使出一招「神龍擺尾」怪腳，no-look取得職業生涯第500球，可是銀河最終仍然以3:5落敗。<br />\n雖然輸波，但達到500球這個里程碑仍然值得慶賀。同樣曾效力銀河、曼聯、巴黎聖日耳門的萬人迷碧咸（David Beckham）就為銀河twitter拍了短片，向伊巴送上祝福，但就寸爆對方。<br />\n碧咸表示：「伊巴，我想說句恭喜。500球，是這麼出色的生涯及球員，很榮幸曾跟你對戰，亦成為你的好友。500球，你真的非常非常老了。還有一樣事情你要改善，你有點害羞，努力吧！」"},{"pid":"f43ff85383e26ca8bac8c2faf0818786a606a3bb","tid":843602,"uid":205587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"一山還有一山高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607818bf4741f56f5fcf5d78d6e1e7eaa39edae7","tid":843602,"uid":209701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15b25507bc92735bf7c49a3747b1c8aefe991c3","tid":843602,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"話時話伊巴去左溫布萊睇波未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda49d51671e0501048e11601bb4cb419836f6df","tid":843602,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 害羞"},{"pid":"a2cfd66020e057eda25f3714495d679b30c3e23b","tid":843602,"uid":195993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"[quote]【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=gyT6NCKs291rbtPbCDDifkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=44c8cc4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://now.com</a>體育】好友就是怎樣說笑也可以。碧咸周一在網上嘲笑攻入500球的伊巴謙莫域真的太老了。<br />\n<br />\n36歲老將伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）周六為洛杉磯銀河作客FC多倫多，使出一招「神龍擺尾」怪腳，no-look取得職業生涯第500球，可是銀河最終仍然以3:5落敗。<br />\n雖然輸波，但達到500球這個里程碑仍然值得慶賀。同樣曾效力銀河、曼聯、巴黎聖日耳門的萬人迷碧咸（David Beckham）就為銀河twitter拍了短片，向伊巴送上祝福，但就寸爆對方。<br />\n碧咸表示：「伊巴，我想說句恭喜。500球，是這麼出色的生涯及球員，很榮幸曾跟你對戰，亦成為你的好友。500球，你真的非常非常老了。還有一樣事情你要改善，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你有點害羞</span></span>，努力吧！"}]}